# Swan Oyster Depot

* 1517 Polk St, San Francisco, CA 94109
* 415-673-1101
* http://places.singleplatform.com/swan-oyster-depot/menu?ref=google
* https://www.sfchronicle.com/food/article/At-Swan-Oyster-Depot-a-secret-menu-built-for-10591335.php

## Notable Dishes
* Sicilian sashimi: Thinly sliced raw salmon, tuna, yellowtail, and scallops drizzled with olive oil and topped with sea salt, pepper, shallots, and capers.
* A Dozen Eggs: A preparation of raw scallops served over ponzu sauce and topped with a dot of Sriracha.
* Crabsanthemum: Dungeness crab leg meat arranged to look like a flower.
* With **olive oil and vinegar sauce**
* Hot Lobster Salad
* Red Eye: A Saturday-morning-only cocktail with Bud Light, cocktail sauce, lemon juice, and other seasonings.
